3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the architect##1
4. the person eating nectarine is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Hobby         | writing   | rock-climbing |
