1. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
2. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
3. the person driving the roller is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate | water    |
| Hobby         | collecting        | singing |
| Pet         | frog          | goat     |
| Transport   | roller        | tram     |

 